trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element for a service to be added to the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en konfigurationselement för en tjänst som ska läggas till workflow runtime engine.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement specifies a host service that should be initialized and activated by the workflow runtime engine.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement anger en värd-tjänst som ska initieras och aktiveras av workflow runtime engine.

trans-unit.source: It corresponds to a host service specified in the <`Services`> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Det motsvarar en värd-tjänst som anges i den `Services`> element i en konfigurationsfil.

trans-unit.source: Because the service specified in a WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement will be initialized by the workflow runtime engine it must have at least one constructor that matches one of the following four signatures (the workflow runtime engine will try to match these signatures in the order shown): Service(WorkflowRuntime runtime, NameValueCollection parameters) Service(WorkflowRuntime runtime) Service(NameValueCollection parameters) Service()
trans-unit.target: Eftersom den tjänst som anges i en WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement initieras av workflow runtime engine måste ha minst en konstruktor som matchar ett av följande fyra (workflow runtime engine försöker matcha dessa signaturer i den ordning som visas): Service(WorkflowRuntime runtime, NameValueCollection parameters) Service(WorkflowRuntime runtime) Service(NameValueCollection parameters) Service()

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Type%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Om du använder den här konstruktorn måste du uttryckligen ställa in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Type%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Type%2A>

trans-unit.source: Called when an unknown attribute is encountered while deserializing the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Anropas när ett okänt attribut påträffades under deserialisering av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The name-value pair specified by name and value is added to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Namn-värdepar som anges av namn och värde har lagts till i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A>samling.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: Any attributes other than `type` that are specified in an <`add`> element to the <`Services`> element in the configuration file are added as a name-value pair to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Attribut än `type` som anges i en `add`> elementet så att den `Services`> element i konfigurationsfilen har lagts till som namn / värde-par till den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A>samling.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Configuration.WorkflowRuntimeServiceElement.Parameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the unrecognized attribute.
The value of the unrecognized attribute.
OnDeserializeUnrecognizedAttribute always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar alltid OnDeserializeUnrecognizedAttribute <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parameters for this service.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar parametrarna för den här tjänsten.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection"></xref> that specifies the parameters for the service.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection"> </xref> som anger parametrarna för tjänsten.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the assembly-qualified type name of the service.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger av sammansättningen kvalificerade typnamnet på tjänsten.

trans-unit.source: The assembly-qualified type name of the service.
An attempt to set Type to a null reference is made.
trans-unit.target: Det görs ett försök att ange en null-referens.
